{
  "stem": "1061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That street was cleared, and we were among the first ones to have to leave our home, and got resettled closer to the-- like there was a square.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then eventually, we found ourselves again in the wrong place, because they were clearing that street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had three more residences, three, after we left our original residence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had three more residences in the same town, but not in an enclosed ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Poles who lived where they lived were allowed to stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "However, the Jews were being squeezed out of certain streets into that other district.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the last place where we lived was-- it was a Christian family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was a teamster.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Had a horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they had a little house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they gave us one big room with a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they had the other part of the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I will never forget-- the wife was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she was working the horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she was washing the horses and feeding them and all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and then I see my mother-- I know that the woman was gonna have a baby.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, I-- I knew just that much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But all of a sudden, mother shushed me and she showed-- she told us to go somewhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she was cooking boiling water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The woman was with the horses five minutes before, and she was giving birth five minutes after.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my mother was attending her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And of course, the children shouldn't know what it was or how it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, because-- Anyhow, so these were people of another-- they were-- they were peasant type, but very decent people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there was a little boy, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I played with him in the snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
